        <row>
          <entry nameend="c2" namest="c1">The following guides are available
          for this component:</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><emphasis role="strong"> <ulink
          url="http://gdp.globus.org/gt4-tutorial/">The Globus Toolkit 4
          Programmer's Tutorial</ulink> </emphasis></entry>

          <entry>Useful tutorial about programming with Web Services in
          GT4.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><emphasis role="strong"> <olink
          targetdoc="securityKey">Security Key Concepts</olink>
          </emphasis></entry>

          <entry>For important general concepts.  [<ulink url="../key/securityKeyConcepts.pdf">pdf</ulink>]</entry>

        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><emphasis role="strong"> <olink
          targetdoc="delegationAdmin">Admin Guide</olink> </emphasis></entry>

          <entry>For system administrators and those installing, building and
          deploying GT. You should already have read the <olink
          targetdoc="gtadmin">Installation Guide</olink> and <olink
          targetdoc="quickstart">Quickstart</olink>.  [<ulink url="admin/delegationAdminGuide.pdf">pdf</ulink>]</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><emphasis role="strong"> <olink
          targetdoc="delegationUser">User's Guide</olink> </emphasis></entry>

          <entry>Describes how end-users typically interact with this
            component. Be sure to also read the <olink targetdoc="gtuser"/>
          for important general information for end-users.  [<ulink url="user/delegationUserGuide.pdf">pdf</ulink>]</entry>

        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><emphasis role="strong"> <olink
          targetdoc="delegationDeveloper">Developer's Guide</olink>
          </emphasis></entry>

          <entry>Reference and usage scenarios for developers.   [<ulink url="developer/delegationDeveloperGuide.pdf">pdf</ulink>]</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry nameend="c2" namest="c1">Other information available for this
          component are:</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><emphasis role="strong"> <olink
          targetdoc="delegationRN">Release Notes</olink> </emphasis></entry>

          <entry>What's new with the <replaceable
          role="entity">version</replaceable> release for this
          component.   [<ulink url="rn/delegationReleaseNotes.pdf">pdf</ulink>]</entry>

        </row>

        <row>
          <entry><emphasis role="strong"> <olink
          targetdoc="delegationPI">Public Interface Guide</olink>
